    <note>Li(2) Kai(4) [26263] Wang Tinggui, WJ, 43.9a-11a (wife, born Duan(1), who died in 1155 at age 84). Not indexed in CBD. A son-in-law, Peng(1) Chunnian, may be the same person as the Taizhou Peng(1) Chunnian [20795], who was active in 1194. However, the Jizhou Peng(1) were numerous and the other identified son-in-laws were all active in the 1150's and 60's, so that a postive identifification is too risky to record. Not indexed in CBD.</note>
